# Synoptic Data API token — Watch Duty's actual weather-vane provider.
#
# With this set, /api/wind queries Synoptic's stations/latest over the region
# bbox across ALL networks (RAWS · CWOP/personal · mesonet · airport) — i.e. the
# full network Watch Duty draws. Without it, the app falls back to the keyless
# NWS feed (ridge RAWS + mesonets only; see app/data/region.ts).
#
# Get a free token from Synoptic's Open Access program:
#   https://synopticdata.com/open-access-program/
#
# Local dev:  copy this file to .env.local and fill in the token (.env.local is
#             gitignored, so the secret never lands in the repo).
# Production: set SYNOPTIC_TOKEN in your Vercel project
#             (Settings → Environment Variables) and redeploy.
#
# Verify a token quickly:  SYNOPTIC_TOKEN=… node scripts/check-synoptic.mjs
SYNOPTIC_TOKEN=
